01:00:46.670 --> 01:00:50.542
And if so, would you contrast
those with your humorous work?

01:00:50.542 --> 01:00:51.500
JOHN CLEESE: Well, yes.

01:00:51.500 --> 01:00:55.640
I did do one very dramatic role.

01:00:55.640 --> 01:00:57.050
I'm going to read it to you.

01:00:57.050 --> 01:00:58.740
Have I got-- oh, yeah.

01:00:58.740 --> 01:00:59.640
Thank you.

01:00:59.640 --> 01:01:01.030
