groups of about 70 or 80.

01:01:26.250 --> 01:01:31.120
And there was the house play
competition every spring term.

01:01:31.120 --> 01:01:36.070
And we decided to do "Faust."

01:01:36.070 --> 01:01:38.640
Two of the boys were
interested in acting,

01:01:38.640 --> 01:01:42.140
so they got the big parts,
Faustus and Mephistopheles.

01:01:42.140 --> 01:01:45.470
I was given the smaller,
but crucial role of Lucifer,

01:01:45.470 --> 01:01:48.640
the Prince Of Darkness,
the embodiment of evil,

01:01:48.640 --> 01:01:51.110
the Antichrist himself.

01:01:51.110 --> 01:01:53.000
Now I realized right
from the start,

01:01:53.000 --> 01:01:55.370
that playing Satan
gave me a chance

01:01:55.370 --> 01:01:57.550
to prove myself as a
serious, straight actor,

01:01:57.550 --> 01:02:01.570
but I'm afraid it
was a devil too far.

01:02:01.570 --> 01:02:04.060
Part of the problem
was my tights.

01:02:04.060 --> 01:02:05.980
Somebody had decided
that in order

01:02:05.980 --> 01:02:08.980
to make my first entrance
as terrifying as possible,

01:02:08.980 --> 01:02:14.590
I should be dressed in
starkest black and tights.

01:02:14.590 --> 01:02:17.870
Now, you know, because I've
related in the book earlier,

01:02:17.870 --> 01:02:20.500
how unmuscular I was, right?

01:02:20.500 --> 01:02:24.520
My legs were so thin, I
could have played a flamingo.

01:02:24.520 --> 01:02:26.600
And yet, the director's
vision involved

01:02:26.600 --> 01:02:30.070
