people, in black tights.

01:02:30.070 --> 01:02:34.820
Now on the day of the
dress rehearsal studio,

01:02:34.820 --> 01:02:38.050
I stood in pitch darkness
behind some black drapes,

01:02:38.050 --> 01:02:39.950
waiting for the cue
for my entrance,

01:02:39.950 --> 01:02:43.590
accompanied by a junior boy,
whose job it was to show me

01:02:43.590 --> 01:02:46.960
where the gap in the drapes
was to be found through which

01:02:46.960 --> 01:02:48.790
I could walk on to stage.

01:02:48.790 --> 01:02:50.990
Then I heard my cue, the
boy parted the curtains

01:02:50.990 --> 01:02:53.930
and I strode forward to
announce my first line which

01:02:53.930 --> 01:02:56.285
was, (DEEP GRAVELLY
VOICE) I am Lucifer.

01:02:59.010 --> 01:03:00.740
Before I had time
to open my mouth,

01:03:00.740 --> 01:03:03.260
