by a wall of laughter

01:03:03.260 --> 01:03:05.080
that shook the building.

01:03:05.080 --> 01:03:06.710
It wasn't just the
tights, of course.

01:03:06.710 --> 01:03:10.270
It was the idea that
this spindly twerp

01:03:10.270 --> 01:03:12.526
could strike terror into
people's hearts, when

01:03:12.526 --> 01:03:14.400
instead of frightening
the shift out of them,

01:03:14.400 --> 01:03:18.030
he was more likely to cause
them to wet their pants.

01:03:18.030 --> 01:03:20.900
Thinking quickly and realizing
the situation was lost,

01:03:20.900 --> 01:03:23.450
I ad-libbed, (DEEP GRAVELLY
VOICE) I am ludicrous.

01:03:26.050 --> 01:03:27.100
Another big laugh.

01:03:27.100 --> 01:03:30.680
Now, later that evening--
that was the dress rehearsal.

01:03:30.680 --> 01:03:35.410
During the actual performance,
things began to go downhill.

01:03:35.410 --> 01:03:38.440
I took up my position
behind the black drapes.

01:03:38.440 --> 01:03:40.640
And this time a different
